Resource        ../lib/ipmi_client.robot
Resource        ../lib/boot_utils.robot
Library         ../lib/ipmi_utils.py

Test Teardown   FFDC On Test Case Fail

Test Tags       Test_Inband_BMC_Auth_Reset

