    [Documentation]  Trigger in-band BMC authentication reset and verify.
    [Tags]  Test_Inband_IPMI_Auth_Reset

    Create Session  openbmc  ${AUTH_URI}  max_retries=1
    ${headers}=  Create Dictionary  Content-Type=application/json
